Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:10.37,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Let me fulfill your small wish together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:15.71,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Ah, of course they will be with us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:50.28,Serifa Std,,0,0,2,,{\fs22.5}I see... So Armony's transmutations weren't failures all this time. They were only dormant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:54.42,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,{\fs26}Oh... she could've become a once-in-a-generation alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:59.42,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,{\fs29.5}When you die... once you're dead, that's the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:24.21,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:56.55,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,It's okay to cry, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:02:00.32,Serifa Std,,0,0,0,,Don’t be ridiculous... Let’s go!
